name: FullyConvolutionalNetworks
description: Constructs a FullyConvolutionalNetwork model with a provided backbone.

properties._description:
model_name (string): Specific variant model of the Faster R-CNN model class, containing fasterrcnn_resnet50_fpn,fasterrcnn_mobilenet_v3_large_320_fpn... 
pretrained (bool): If True, returns a model pre-trained on ImageNet
progress (bool): If True, displays a progress bar of the download to stderr
num_classes (int): Number of categories
